    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it feels so fake though. like, people talking about \"small actions\" when the math just doesn't add up. it feels like being told to rearrange the deck chairs on the titanic. i look at the climate data and i just feel like there's no escape from the trajectory we're on. it's hard to see why any struggle is worth it when the outcome is already decided. it just feels like a waiting game for something terrible.",
